DNS (GODADDY)
ACM


ACM
        Request public certificate
            Fully qualified Domain name = *.<domain-name.com>

        Validation Method = DNS Validation

        Tag key = Name,  Tag value = <domain-name.com>
                          ===create

Refresh to see the certificate... click on it to validate the ACM With GODADDY

GODADDY --> Manage DNS --> ADD NEW RECORD

TYPE = CNAME,  NAME = ACM (cname Name) note to take out the domain name at the end, Value = ACM (Value name) note to take out the . at the end save it.